name: AppLocalizations
desc:
Callers can lookup localized strings with an instance of AppLocalizations
returned by AppLocalizations.of(context).

name: localizationsDelegates
desc:
A list of this localizations delegate along with the default localizations
delegates.

name: supportedLocales
desc: A list of this localizations delegate's supported locales.

name: InitializationGate
desc: A gatekeeper widget that manages the app's initialization lifecycle.

name: createState
desc: Creates the mutable state for this widget at a given location in the tree.

name: onInit
desc: The asynchronous initialization logic to execute.

name: PortfolioApp
desc: The root widget of the application.

name: build
desc: Describes the part of the user interface represented by this widget.

name: main
desc: The main entry point for the Portfolio application.
